## Overview

pihole is an open source, self-hosted DNS sinkhole that can be installed on a raspberry pi device. pihole blocks advertisements and trackers network-wide through DNS query management. 
pihole is configured with a static IP for consistent DNS resolutions and provides an administrator dashboard for real time monitoring, block statistics, and other pertinent settings.

